## Deployment Notes

### What Happens on Vercel Deployment
1. The Analytics component will automatically track page views
2. New routes will be added at `/_vercel/insights/*`
3. You should see a Fetch/XHR request to `/_vercel/insights/view` in the browser's Network tab
4. Analytics data will be available in the Vercel dashboard under the Analytics tab

### Next Steps for the User
1. **Enable Analytics in Vercel Dashboard**:
   - Go to your project on Vercel
   - Click the "Analytics" tab
   - Click "Enable" if not already enabled

2. **Deploy to Vercel**:
   - Run `vercel deploy` or push to the connected Git repository
   - Analytics will start tracking visitors automatically

3. **View Analytics Data**:
   - Navigate to your Vercel dashboard
   - Select your project
   - Click the "Analytics" tab to view metrics

